  {name: "Artspace", num_employees: nil, total_money_raised: "$12.2M", twitter_username: "artspace", category_code: "ecommerce", city: "New York", twitter_followers: nil, career_page_link: nil, year_founded: nil, overview: "At Artspace, they&#8217;re changing the way the world experiences art. Their mission is to help collectors and aspiring collectors discover, learn about and collect fine art. Their curators collaborate with top museums, galleries and cultural institutions to provide the best collection of contemporary art in the world. They offer limited editions and original works from the most recognized artists to rising stars and make them available for sale online, at affordable prices. Membership is free and grants their subscribers first access to their most coveted limited editions, enabling them to preview and collect these exclusive works before anyone else."},
