  {name: "Pictorious", num_employees: nil, total_money_raised: "$25k", twitter_username: "Pictorious", category_code: "photo_video", city: "New York", twitter_followers: nil, career_page_link: nil, year_founded: 2011, overview: "Pictorious combines fun social game mechanics with the ubiquitous activity of photo-sharing. You might think of it as Instagram meets Draw Something.\n\nOn Pictorious, users create fun challenges for their friends. Their friends then post photos as proof that they&#8217;ve stepped up and completed the challenge. Players level up and earn rewards as they complete challenges and receive likes.\n\nPictorious is a community of people who love experiencing new things, meeting new people and exploring new places."},
