  {name: "TheLadders", num_employees: 110, total_money_raised: "$7.25M", twitter_username: "TheLadders", category_code: "web", city: "New York", twitter_followers: nil, career_page_link: nil, year_founded: 2003, overview: "With more than 6 million members, TheLadders is the premier online job-matching service committed to finding the right person for the right job since 2003. Its groundbreaking iPhone app generated more than 100,000 downloads in its first week. Originally recognized as the leading job-matching site for high-earning professionals, TheLadders expanded its services in fall 2011 to all career-driven professionals. In doing so, the more than 43,000 employers and recruiters that use TheLadders to source qualified candidates now have access to professionals at all levels, free of charge. TheLadders is headquartered in New York City. For more information, visit TheLaddersBlog and TheLadders.com. Your career is our job.™"},
