  {link: "https://www.smartrecruiters.com/AppboyInc/74187403-web-software-developer", title: "WEB SOFTWARE DEVELOPER", full_text: "Web Software Developer New York, NY Company Description Appboy is a rapidly growing analytics and marketing automation platform for mobile apps. Job Description Appboy is looking for a web developer to help build and maintain our many online assets, including our website, blog, documentation sites, and more. You'll work closely with our Success Squad and Marketing teams to enhance the public face of Appboy and create a first class experience for our clients. We use a diverse technology stack across our online presence. Candidates should have previous experience with software and product design, be able to intelligently discuss their design decisions, and a passion for getting things done. Since this role will entail working closely with different stakeholders on a wide variety of technologies, excellent communication skills and the ability to rapidly learn new technologies are also a must. ResponsibilitiesContribute to Appboy's public-facing websites and web assets (landing pages, etc.).Work closely with our Marketing and Success Squad teams to enhance Appboy's client-facing sites and provide an excellent experience for our clients.Maintain knowledge freshness and identify feature opportunities and evolving best practices for our web stack. Qualifications Experience with functional languages and MVC frameworks such as Ruby on Rails or Python/Django.Experience with frontend languages and modern web technologies.Strong sense of excellent user experience and an eye for quality design. An ability and willingness to rapidly dive in and use new technologies.(Bonus) Experience with Wordpress or other common blogging / content delivery solutions. Posted by Kevin Wang share this job The free social recruiting platform Learn more", is_draft: true, company_id: 56, dept: "Engineering", years_exp: 1, sub_dept: "Back-End", description: nil, key_phrase